{"article_id":"PkxxYhlQdqKIyKmW","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Democrats dug in their heels Sunday on President Trump ' s threat","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"to shut down the government","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"unless he gets money for his border wall ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"saying","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"if the president makes good on his demand ,","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"the American people will suffer .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"But the White House contends","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"American citizens are already suffering","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"- with or without a shutdown -","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"because of the rise in illegal immigration .","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"The two sides showed no sign of willingness to compromise Sunday ,","depth":4},{"id":11,"text":"with just four days left","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"to broker an agreement","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"before the federal government partially shuts down .","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"\" We should not let a temper tantrum","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"- threats -","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"push us in the direction","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"of doing something","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"even our Republican colleagues know","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"is wrong , \"","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"Senate Minority Leader Charles E. Schumer told NBC .","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"The New York Democrat said","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"Republicans in Congress \" have to have the guts \"","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"to tell the president","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"he ' s wrong","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"for refusing to fund the government","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"unless he gets $ 5 billion for his border wall .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"\" President Trump should understand","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"there are not the votes for the wall in the House or the Senate .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"He is not going to get the wall in any form , \"","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"And the top Democrat on the House Oversight and Government Reform Committee Rep. Elijah Cummings , Maryland Democrat , said","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"voters want the government to help them ,","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"not hurt them ,","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"suggesting","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"a shutdown will politically damage Republicans .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"\" Whenever I hear a president say to the American people at Christmastime ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"' I am going to shut down your government , '","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"it pains me","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"because I know","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"it ' s going to make a bad Christmas for a lot of people , \"","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"he told CNN .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"But White House adviser Stephen Miller said","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Mr. Trump will do \" whatever is necessary \"","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"to get the money","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"to build the border wall .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"\" They can either choose to fight for Americans","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"- working class -","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"or to promote illegal immigration .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"You can ' t do both , \"","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Mr. Miller said of Democrats in an interview Sunday with CBS .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"Congress is running up against a Friday deadline","depth":4},{"id":52,"text":"to finish funding the government ,","depth":4},{"id":53,"text":"with several news reports suggesting","depth":4},{"id":54,"text":"they may look to a short-term \" continuing resolution \"","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"that funds the government at current levels","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"to get them past the holidays and into the new year .","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"Sen. Susan Collins , Maine Republican , told ABC","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"she wants to see lawmakers take up a proposal","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"that provided $ 2.5 billion this year and over the next 10 years for border security ,","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"which would fund a border fence , increase technology and patrol agents along the southern border .","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"\" There is absolutely no excuse","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"to shut down government on this issue or any issue .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"I have suggested","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"we revisit a compromise proposal","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"we brought forward earlier this year , \"","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"she said on Sunday ,","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"breaking with her party ' s leader .","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"House Minority Leader Rep. Nancy Pelosi and Mr. Schumer have offered Mr. Trump two other options ,","depth":5},{"id":69,"text":"and they both include some money","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"- roughly $ 1.3 billion -","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"for the wall .","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"But it remains unclear whether the president will accept any compromise after his televised stand off with the two Democratic leaders in the Oval Office last week ,","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"where he demanded the $ 5 billion","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"and claimed","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"he isn ' t afraid to shut down the government .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"\" I am proud to shut down the government for border security , \"","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"Mr. Trump said .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":155,"left":128,"right":154,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":128,"left":87,"right":127,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":87,"left":83,"right":86,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":83,"left":80,"right":82,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":0,"right":79,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":82,"left":3,"r